            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">3/4/89. ¶  ¶ May I advise, dear Dr Bride, that this important publication be purchased for the public Library. ¶ Regardfully your ¶  ¶ Ferd. von Mueller....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">89.04.03b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Bride</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. P89-436, Unit 142, VPRS 805, inward correspondence VA 913, Public Library of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3/4/89.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May I advise, dear Dr Bride, that this important publication be purchased for the public Library.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The cover on the file reveals that the work recommended by M was Franchet (1889-90). The Library sub-committee approved the purchase on 30 July 1889. By 3 August the book had been ordered and M had been 'informed thereof'. The work does not, however, appear in the Library’s present-day catalogue.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
